{"tid":342423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估城市]女遊客玩動感影院　座椅升至10米時墮斃","createTime":"2017-07-31T14:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T15:11:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22d97da448f48b608edf8986f9c8a876f2781f07","tid":342423,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170731/s00004/1501500011564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170731%2Fs00004%2F1501500011564&d=7xwA1LCTBZptFpxobPm7rqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b3c20226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170731%2Fs00004%2F1501500011564&h=af9511aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170731/s00004/1501500011564</a><br />\n<br />\n女遊客在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">北京</span>遊樂場玩飛行動感影院時，從10米高的座椅摔下，即場死亡。當地媒體報道，死者51歲，山西人，警察已初步排除人為傷害，正調查事故原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北京昌平樂多港奇幻樂園的醫務室值班醫生指，昨日下午2時，飛行影院發生遊客墜落事件，他到場後發現有一名女子躺在地上，身邊很多血，當時已沒有生命迹象了。<br />\n<br />\n根據官網介紹，飛行影院「翱翔紫禁」是集球幕電影、大型機械控制、實時現場特效等多種高科技手段於一身的項目，遊客經由平立式座椅系統提升至10多米高空觀看壯觀的電影畫面，體驗在宏大場景中凌空飛行的刺激感受。<br />\n<br />\n「翱翔紫禁」每場容納100人，一場時間約6分鐘，每日接待2400人，已暫停開放。"},{"pid":"164d779cd1226951bc8cc9dd426ff21df8f49bcf","tid":342423,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"支那狗-1"},{"pid":"0c958a8037b09c6c561d80821d05a6c599d6804e","tid":342423,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"每場容納100人<br />\n每日接待2400人<br />\n咁點解得佢一個死？"},{"pid":"b35ab2b80a923f1763ed6d6e144b1727d40e575f","tid":342423,"uid":7477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"幾真實wor又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398cd4fe8a0dfbad87fabb1ebd988b0fa751bf1c","tid":342423,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"坐跳樓機睇戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72eb24083f59933d83b876d4b945f795a1fd997d","tid":342423,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"係鬼國捱左51年先死<br />\n早死早超生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf9bce8d1c901049d4cdf6873ef9c4b57988693","tid":342423,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"細個係東莞玩過海盜船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}